[[詹姆斯·卡梅隆|詹姆斯·卡梅隆]]是加拿大[[电影导演|电影导演]]、[[编剧|编剧]]兼[[制片人|制片人]]，在电影和电视领域有广泛涉猎。卡梅隆的处女作是1978年的[[科幻电影|科幻]][[短片|短片]]《克赛诺起源》（{{lang|en|''Xenogenesis''}}），他亲自担任导演、编剧和制片人<ref name="pir"> {{cite book | last1 = Clarke | first1 = James | title = The Cinema of James Cameron: Bodies in Heroic Motion | date = 2014-05-14 | publisher = Columbia University Press | location = Chichester, New York | isbn = 978-0231169776 | page = 7}}</ref><ref name="loc">{{cite web | url = http://www.loc.gov/today/pr/2008/08-237.html | title = 2008 entries to National Film Registry Announced | publisher = Library of Congress | date = 2008-12-30 | accessdate = 2015-01-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141101034925/http://www.loc.gov/today/pr/2008/08-237.html | archivedate = 2014-11-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。卡梅隆从业早期做过各种技术性工作，如视觉特技制作、梳妆台助手、亚光画师和摄影师。他导演的首部长片电影是[[1981年电影|1981年]]上映的《[[食人鱼2：繁殖|食人鱼2：繁殖]]》（{{lang|en|''Piranha II: The Spawning''}}）<ref name="loc" /><ref>{{cite book | last1 = Clarke | first1 = James | title = The Cinema of James Cameron: Bodies in Heroic Motion | date = 2014-05-14 | publisher = Columbia University Press | location = Chichester, New York | isbn = 978-0231169776 | page = 100}}</ref>。接下来他又执导了[[1984年电影|1984年]]的科幻[[动作电影|动作]][[惊悚片|惊悚片]]《[[终结者|终结者]]》，[[阿诺·施瓦辛格|阿诺·施瓦辛格]]主演，这是两人的首度合作，也是卡梅隆的成名作<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141223134102/http://projects.latimes.com/hollywood/star-walk/james-cameron/ | deadurl = no | url = http://projects.latimes.com/hollywood/star-walk/james-cameron/ | title = James Cameron | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | accessdate = 2015-01-15 | archivedate = 2014-12-23 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last1 = Sickel | first1 = Robert | title = American Film in the Digital Age | date = 2010-12-08 | publisher = Praeger | location = Santa Barbara, California | isbn = 978-0275998622 | page = 115}}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last1 = Clarke | first1 = James | title = The Cinema of James Cameron: Bodies in Heroic Motion | date = 2014-05-14 | publisher = Columbia University Press | location = Chichester, New York | isbn = 978-0231169776 | page = 2}}</ref>。1986年，他编剧并导演的科幻动作[[续集|续集]]电影《[[异形2|异形2]]》上映，出演[[异形_(电影)|前作]]的[[西格妮·韦弗|西格妮·韦弗]]再次担任女主角<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9A0DE7DA1731F93BA25754C0A960948260 | title = Aliens (1986) | work = The New York Times | publisher = Arthur Ochs Sulzberger | last = Goodman | first = Walter | date = 1986-07-18 | accessdate = 2015-01-15 | archivedate = 2014-11-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141129225824/http://www.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9A0DE7DA1731F93BA25754C0A960948260 }}</ref>。接下来他又导演了另一部科幻片《[[深渊_(电影)|深渊]]》。1991年，卡梅隆推出《终结者》的续集《[[终结者2：审判日|终结者2：审判日]]》，施瓦辛格回归出演男主角<ref>{{cite news | url = http://articles.latimes.com/1991-07-03/entertainment/ca-1467_1_arnold-schwarzenegger | title = Movie Review: He Said He'd Be Back...: Arnold and 'Terminator 2' Return With a Vengeance | work = Los Angeles Times | publisher = Austin Beutner | date = 1991-07-03 | last = Turan | first = Kenneth | accessdate = 2015-01-16 | archive-date = 2014-12-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141215043142/http://articles.latimes.com/1991-07-03/entertainment/ca-1467_1_arnold-schwarzenegger | dead-url = no }}</ref>，这年他还为动作犯罪片《[[惊爆点|惊爆点]]》担任[[执行制片人|执行制片人]]。3年后，卡梅隆执导了第3部由施瓦辛格主演的电影《[[真实的谎言|真实的谎言]]》<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9905E6D91E38F934A25754C0A962958260 | title = True Lies (1994) | work = The New York Times | publisher = Arthur Ochs Sulzberger Jr. | last = James | first = Caryn | date = 1994-07-17 | accessdate = 2015-01-15 | archivedate = 2014-12-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141222194654/http://www.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9905E6D91E38F934A25754C0A962958260 }}</ref>。

1997年，编剧、导演并亲自担任制片人的[[爱情片|爱情]][[灾难片|灾难片]]《[[泰坦尼克号_(1997年电影)|泰坦尼克号]]》上映，全球[[票房|票房]]超过18.4亿美元<ref>{{cite news | title = The Billion Dollar film club | work = The Daily Telegraph | publisher = Telegraph Media Group | date = 2011-08-01 | accessdate = 2015-01-15 | archivedate = 2014-03-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140322043048/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/harry-potter/8674770/The-Billion-Dollar-film-club.html | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/harry-potter/8674770/The-Billion-Dollar-film-club.html }}</ref>{{#tag:ref|2012年，该片在全球发行3{{lang|en|D}}版本，把总票房数额提升到21.8亿美元<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150107181254/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=titanic.htm | archivedate = 2015-01-07 | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=titanic.htm | title = Titanic (1997) | publisher = Box Office Mojo. Amazon.com | accessdate = 2015-01-15 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Titanic 3D (2012) | publisher = Box Office Mojo. Amazon.com | accessdate = 2015-01-05 | archivedate = 2014-11-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109084054/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=titanic3d.htm | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=titanic3d.htm }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=releases&id=titanic3d.htm | title = Titanic 3D (2012) | publisher = Box Office Mojo. Amazon.com | accessdate = 2015-01-15 | archive-date = 2014-11-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141109100803/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=releases&id=titanic3d.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。|group="注"}}，刷新了世界电影票房纪录{{#tag:ref|2010年，卡梅隆执导的3{{lang|en|D}}科幻片《[[阿凡达|阿凡达]]》打破了《泰坦尼克号》所创下的纪录<ref name="high">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141101121133/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/8482058.stm | archivedate = 2014-11-01 | deadurl = no | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/8482058.stm | title = Avatar overtakes Titanic as top-grossing film ever | publisher = BBC News | date = 2010-01-27 | accessdate = 2015-01-15 }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。卡梅隆则在[[第70届奥斯卡金像奖|第70届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]上获得[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]、[[奥斯卡最佳导演奖|导演]]和[[奥斯卡最佳影片剪辑奖|剪辑]]3项大奖。影片一共得到14项提名，追平了1950年的[[剧情片|剧情片]]《[[彗星美人|彗星美人]]》所创纪录；最终11项获奖又追平了1959年史诗剧情片《[[賓漢|賓漢]]》的纪录<ref>{{cite news | title = 'Titanic' tally ties Oscar record | work = Variety | publisher = Penske Media Corporation | last = Gray | first = Tim | accessdate = 2015-01-15 | date = 1998-03-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150106061819/http://variety.com/1998/more/news/titanic-tally-ties-oscar-record-2-1117469068/ | url = http://variety.com/1998/more/news/titanic-tally-ties-oscar-record-2-1117469068/ | archivedate = 2015-01-06 }}</ref>。卡梅隆还在[[第55届金球奖|第55届金球奖]]角逐中拿下了[[金球奖最佳戏剧类影片|最佳影片奖（正剧类）]]和[[金球奖最佳导演|最佳导演奖]]<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1998/01/19/movies/titanic-wins-top-golden-globe-award.html | title = 'Titanic' Wins Top Golden Globe Award | work = The New York Times | publisher = Arthur Ochs Sulzberger, Jr. | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141222194644/http://www.nytimes.com/1998/01/19/movies/titanic-wins-top-golden-globe-award.html | last = Sterngold | first = James | date = 1998-01-19 | accessdate = 2015-01-15 | archivedate = 2014-12-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。接下来他导演并监制了两部水下题材纪录片，分别是[[2003年电影|2003年]]的《深渊幽灵》（{{lang|en|''Ghosts of the Abyss''}}）和2005年的《深海异形》（{{lang|en|''Aliens of the Deep''}}）。[[2009年电影|2009年]]的3{{lang|en|D}}科幻片《[[阿凡达|阿凡达]]》是卡梅隆自《泰坦尼克号》后执导的首部长片电影，刷新了前作保持十余年的世界电影票房纪录，截至2014年，这一纪录仍然保持<ref name="high" /><ref>{{cite web | url = http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=avatar.htm | title = Avatar (2009) | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150115060024/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=avatar.htm | publisher = Box Office Mojo. Amazon.com | accessdate = 2015-01-16 | archivedate = 2015-01-15 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。《阿凡达》在[[第82届奥斯卡金像奖|第82届奥斯卡金像奖]]角逐中获得9项提名，最终在3个技术类奖项上胜出<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-12-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141222182847/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/SHOWBIZ/Movies/03/07/academy.awards.night/ | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2010/SHOWBIZ/Movies/03/07/academy.awards.night/ | title = 'Hurt Locker' is best picture, wins six Oscars | publisher = CNN | date = 2010-03-09 | accessdate = 2015-01-16 | last = Duke | first = Alan | deadurl = no }}</ref>。卡梅隆还在[[第67届金球奖|第67届金球奖]]角逐中再度赢得最佳导演和最佳影片奖（正剧类）<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141222184559/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/SHOWBIZ/TV/01/17/golden.globes/ | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2010/SHOWBIZ/TV/01/17/golden.globes/ | title = 'Avatar' wins two Golden Globes | publisher = CNN | date = 2010-01-18 | last = Duke | first = Alan | accessdate = 2015-01-16 | archivedate = 2014-12-22 }}</ref>。此后他先后在多部影片制作过程中出任执行制片人，分别是[[2011年电影|2011年]]的《[[夺命深渊|夺命深渊]]》和[[2012年电影|2012年]]的《太阳马戏团：遥远的世界》（{{lang|en|''Cirque du Soleil: Worlds Away''}}），还有[[2014年电影|2014年]]的纪录片《深海挑战者号3D》（{{lang|en|''Deepsea Challenge 3D''}}）。

卡梅隆首次现身电视荧屏是1998年的[[情景喜剧|情景喜剧]]《我为卿狂》（{{lang|en|''Mad About You''}}）。两年后，他担任执行制片人的科幻题材[[电视剧|电视剧]]《[[末世黑天使|末世黑天使]]》在[[美国电影|美国]]播出，该剧由[[杰西卡·阿尔芭|杰西卡·阿尔芭]]主演。2005年，他在两部有关[[泰坦尼克号沉船事故|泰坦尼克号沉船事故]]的[[纪录片|纪录片]]中亮相，分别是《泰坦尼克号的最后谜团》（{{lang|en|''Last Mysteries of the Titanic''}}）和《托尼·罗宾逊的泰坦尼克号历险记》（{{lang|en|''Tony Robinson's Titanic Adventure''}}）。同年，卡梅隆还在喜剧剧集《[[明星伙伴|明星伙伴]]》中以真实身份出镜，此后又为两部[[圣经|圣经]]题材纪录片担任执行制片人，分别是2006年的《[[解密出埃及记|解密出埃及记]]》（{{lang|en|''The Exodus Decoded''}}）和2007年的《[[失落的耶稣之墓|失落的耶稣之墓]]》（{{lang|en|''Lost Tomb of Jesus''}}）。2012年，他担任执行制片人并在其中出镜的《詹姆斯·卡梅隆：再见泰坦尼克》发行，这已是他参与制作的第3部和泰坦尼克号有关的纪录片。两年后，卡梅隆担任气象变化题材电视剧《[[多灾凶年|多灾凶年]]》（{{lang|en|''Years of Living Dangerously''}}）面世，该剧获得[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]杰出纪录片或非虚构类剧集奖<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150101160429/http://www.emmys.com/shows/years-living-dangerously | deadurl = no | url = http://www.emmys.com/shows/years-living-dangerously | title = Years of Living Dangerously | publisher = Academy of Television Arts & Sciences | accessdate = 2015-01-16 | archivedate = 2015-01-01 }}</ref>。

